data.description: ***OWNED SOLAR** Welcome to your dream home in beautiful Casa Grande, AZ! This 4 bedroom, 2 bath home boasts 2708 sq ft of luxurious living space with an open floor plan perfect for entertaining. The exterior of the home features solar screens on the windows, providing energy efficiency and added privacy. Plus, you'll love spending your days relaxing in the sparkling pool or lounging under the raised poolside pergola. Perfect for outdoor gatherings, the home also includes a built-in outside BBQ. Inside, you'll find a newer AC unit and a security system for peace of mind. Need to access the attic? No problem, this home includes ladder access to the attic. And for extra convenience, there are outside electrical outlets around the house and yard. Start living your best life in Casa Grande, A
